name: SetSpawn
body:
![SetSpawn](http://i.imgur.com/nPW4x7q.png)

### Commands and Permissions
| Command   | Permission        | Additional informations |
|-----------|-------------------|-------------------------|
| /spawn    | setspawn.spawn    | Teleports you to Spawn  |
| /setspawn | setspawn.setspawn | Sets spawn point        |
| /rspawn   | setspawn.rspawn   | Reloads SetSpawn        |
| *         | setspawn.*        |                         |
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
